                output_val = json.loads(response.content, cls=rest_funcs.NumPyDecoder)['result']
                output_val_uni=json.loads(output_val, cls=rest_funcs.NumPyDecoder)
                for key, value in output_val_uni.items():
                    setattr(self, key, value)
